---

<Layout
  title="The Real Cost of Importing Commodities from Africa (Full Breakdown) | Origin Direct Group"
  description="Complete line-by-line cost breakdown for importing commodities from Africa. Real example: 20MT cashew nuts from Ghana to Rotterdam with every cost element explained."
  structuredData={[articleSchema, breadcrumbSchema]}
>
  <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
